cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":401301,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"…とにかく、訳も分からないまま@手を出したくないんだ…！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":401201,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"御崎 海香","textLeft":"ごめんなさい…@無茶苦茶なこと言って…"},{"chara":[{"id":100301}],"textRight":"…ううう～…"},{"bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":100301,"motion":101}],"textRight":"…うん、分かった！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":401301,"motion":400,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"牧 カオル","textLeft":"え!?@…そ、そうなの？"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story06","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100301,"motion":0}],"textRight":"この街って、訳わからないこと@だらけだからね！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100301}],"textRight":"こういうことも@日常茶飯事ってやつだから…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100301}],"textRight":"答えはシンプルにした方が@案外解決しやすいんだ"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":100301,"motion":200}],"textRight":"つまり、この場合…"},{"chara":[{"id":100301,"motion":0}],"textRight":"「何が起きたか調べよう」@「分かるまで手出しはしない」"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100301,"motion":201}],"textRight":"…だね！"},{"chara":[{"id":401301,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"そ、そう、だね…！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":401201,"lipSynch":0,"motion":1,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"御崎 海香","textLeft":"（…日常茶飯事…なんだ…）","turnEffect":"thinking"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":401201,"lipSynch":0}],"textLeft":"（…あすなろ市とは、また大分@事情が違っているみたいね…）"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100301,"motion":101}],"textRight":"で！で！どうすんの！@こうなったらわたしも手伝うよ！","turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":401301,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"牧 カオル","textLeft":"え、ホントに!?"},{"chara":[{"id":100301,"motion":0}],"textRight":"乗りかかった船ってやつだし…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100301}],"textRight":"わたしも本物のかずみは@好きだからねっ！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401201,"motion":100,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"御崎 海香","textLeft":"…ありがとう！@お言葉に甘えるわ！"},{"chara":[{"id":401201}],"textLeft":"私たち、あすなろ市から来て@この街の事情に疎いから…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100301,"motion":200}],"textRight":"あすなろ市！@だから知らない顔なんだ！"},{"chara":[{"id":401201,"motion":200}],"textLeft":"私は御崎海香"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401301,"motion":100,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"牧 カオル","textLeft":"牧カオルだよ！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100301,"motion":101}],"textRight":"わたしは…！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401201,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"御崎 海香","textLeft":"由比鶴乃…だよね？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100301}],"textRight":"おー！@何で知ってるの!?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401301,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"牧 カオル","textLeft":"…さっき言ってたから…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100301,"motion":0}],"textRight":"…あ、そっかー！@なはは…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100301,"motion":0}],"textRight":"…で、どうしよっか？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":401201,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"御崎 海香","textLeft":"こうして鶴乃さんに…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100301}],"textRight":"鶴乃でいいよ！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401201,"motion":100}],"textLeft":"…うん…！@…鶴乃に出会えたから…"},{"chara":[{"id":401201}],"textLeft":"神浜のこと@色々と聞かせてほしいの"},{"chara":[{"id":100301,"motion":200}],"textRight":"いいよ！@何でも聞いてよ！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":401301,"motion":300,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"牧 カオル","textLeft":"でも、ここじゃ@いつあのかずみに見つかるか…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":100301,"motion":300}],"textRight":"ふーむ…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100301,"motion":101}],"textRight":"だったら、話をするには@バッチリの場所があるよ！"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}